1
00:00:09,790 --> 00:00:11,000
For you to come today,

2
00:00:11,210 --> 00:00:12,500
despite your busy schedule,

3
00:00:12,500 --> 00:00:13,670
I am truly grateful.

4
00:00:13,790 --> 00:00:14,790
On such an important occasion,

5
00:00:14,830 --> 00:00:15,830
to be able to share it with you,

6
00:00:16,000 --> 00:00:17,000
I'm deeply honored.

7
00:00:17,330 --> 00:00:18,330
Congratulations.

8
00:00:18,500 --> 00:00:20,380
A grand party like this
suits you well.

9
00:00:20,920 --> 00:00:22,040
Don't let up now.

10
00:00:22,460 --> 00:00:23,830
Keep up the good work.

11
00:00:24,500 --> 00:00:26,380
You're too kind.
I'm not worthy of such praise.

12
00:00:26,500 --> 00:00:27,500
One day,

13
00:00:27,500 --> 00:00:28,750
I will become someone
worthy of your expectations.

14
00:00:32,670 --> 00:00:33,710
I'm looking forward to it.

15
00:00:36,790 --> 00:00:38,750
This feels incredible.

16
00:00:41,080 --> 00:00:43,880
The president of one of Japan's
leading corporations,

17
00:00:43,880 --> 00:00:46,080
the head of Kurogane Holdings,

18
00:00:46,080 --> 00:00:47,830
personally came
to my birthday party.

19
00:00:47,880 --> 00:00:49,960
And he even said he has high hopes for me.

20
00:00:51,750 --> 00:00:53,170
This is just too good!

21
00:00:56,710 --> 00:00:57,790
It's almost time.

22
00:00:59,790 --> 00:01:00,790
But before that,

23
00:01:01,000 --> 00:01:03,210
there's something I need
to take care of.

24
00:01:03,630 --> 00:01:05,250
That video
the president asked for.

25
00:01:05,290 --> 00:01:06,500
It's all ready.

26
00:01:07,250 --> 00:01:08,960
With this,
those two are finished.

27
00:01:09,420 --> 00:01:11,710
The cheating woman and her victim.

28
00:01:12,670 --> 00:01:16,080
The media will spin it as
the tragedy of a handsome entrepreneur.

29
00:01:16,500 --> 00:01:19,170
And with that, my status
will rise even higher.
